| 1 | **Bus log not drained at init** | First `next` returns player setup logs (AddTask/AddAchievement) |
| 2 | **Auto-equip doesn't consume bag items** | Items 3001/3002 remain in bag after auto-equip |
| 3 | **Unequip empty slot = silent no-op** | No error or log when unequipping an empty slot |
| 4 | **collector_100 name misleading** | Checks unlocked achievements ≥ 2, not item count ≥ 100 |
